lang=\"EN-US\">If your host gets offended when you ask for salt\nduring a meal, in which country are you?</span></p>\n\n<span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br></span></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">Dec. 1<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">In the Netherlands, at a birthday party, who do you congratulate?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">________________________________</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font>From <b>December 1st to December 20th</b>, join us for a fun and engaging daily challenge!<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font>This year, our quiz is all about <b>interculturality</b>—exploring cultures, traditions, and perspectives from around the world.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font>&nbsp;</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><font><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;;\">💡</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"> <b>How it works:</b><o:p></o:p></span></font></p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-top: 0cm;\" type=\"disc\"><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font>Each day at <b>12:00 PM</b>, a new question will be posted on the <b>ILC app on top of this message as well as on the door of room A262</b>.<o:p></o:p></font></span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font>Be the first to answer correctly via the following form&nbsp;<a href=\"https://forms.office.com/e/qVR5ThM3j1\"><font color=\"#0e57cd\"><u>https://forms.office.com/e/qVR5ThM3j1</u></font></a> to win a surprise reward!<o:p></o:p></font></span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font>The correct answer and the name of the daily winner will be revealed <b>the next day</b>, along with the next question.&nbsp; Come &amp; visit us in A262 to get your treat!</font></span></li></ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 36pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font>&nbsp;</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><font><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">Test your knowledge, speed, and wit. Will you be the fastest? </span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;;\">🏆</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">